1
00:00:00,807 --> 00:00:02,969
In 1857

2
00:00:02,994 --> 00:00:05,651
The church was established as is known

3
00:00:05,676 --> 00:00:11,406
But many changes and renovations were made to it

4
00:00:11,431 --> 00:00:15,651
The church’s style did not remain that of the 18th century

5
00:00:15,676 --> 00:00:18,151
But in 1960

6
00:00:18,176 --> 00:00:20,521
It was built and expanded

7
00:00:20,546 --> 00:00:24,531
Two families bought two adjacent houses

8
00:00:24,556 --> 00:00:26,510
In order to expand the church

9
00:00:26,535 --> 00:00:28,411
Two houses next to the church

10
00:00:28,436 --> 00:00:30,130
To expand the church

11
00:00:30,155 --> 00:00:32,552
These additions appeared

12
00:00:32,577 --> 00:00:35,365
The administrative wing, the priest’s house

13
00:00:35,390 --> 00:00:40,416
And other rooms as halls for teaching the Armenian language

14
00:00:40,441 --> 00:00:43,620
And for church gatherings

15
00:00:43,870 --> 00:00:48,062
In addition to a hall I remember was for Christmas celebrations

16
00:00:48,297 --> 00:00:52,046
Where Santa Claus came and gave gifts to the parish children
